Class SwerveDrivetrain.SwerveDriveState

java.lang.Object
com.ctre.phoenix6.swerve.SwerveDrivetrain.SwerveDriveState
All Implemented Interfaces:

Enclosing class:
SwerveDrivetrain<DriveMotorT extends CommonTalon,SteerMotorT extends CommonTalon,EncoderT extends ParentDevice>
public static class SwerveDrivetrain.SwerveDriveState extends Object implements Cloneable
Plain-Old-Data class holding the state of the swerve drivetrain. This encapsulates most data that is relevant for telemetry or decision-making from the Swerve Drive.
